      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"letting go of the weight\"... that sounds almost peaceful. like, instead of this constant struggle to exist where you don't belong, you just... fade out. and the best part is that nobody would even feel the loss, because no one really saw me in the first place. it's like a quiet exit. i guess i'm just wondering if it's even wrong to want that kind of peace.",
